    "number": 4,
    "name": "Maria Fernandez",
    "relationship": "",
    "text": "I was six years old when Mary came into my life. Larry took her to his prom. I remember that day like it was yesterday - especially the two of them pulling away in the orange pinto! One of my most special memories was the first Christmas Mary spent with our family. The photo is not very clear but she made me a flannel night gown that was a light blue floral print. I literally wore it out - until there were holes and I could not wear it any more. I don\u2019t consider Mary an in-law, she is another one of my sisters.",
