    "relationship": "",
    "text": "We each raised our 3 kids side by side and there are too many great memories to count. Among the highlights are the joint family vacations and none stands out more than Nantucket. The memories stay forever in our hearts -- from the caravan drive up to Cape Cod from Virginia, to all of us piling into the house on York Street, to dinners in the backyard and days on the beach.  We sure have a long list of beautiful shared memories.",
